</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="c1">// 첫 번째와 마지막 요소 확인</span>
<span class="n">println</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">arr</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">first</span><span class="o">())</span>
